Fabricato Says It Paid Down Bankruptcy Debt to 5.5 Billion Pesos

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-05-24T21:55:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/fabricato-says-it-paid-down-bankruptcy-debt-to-5-5-billion-pesos.html
Fabricato SA,  Colombia ’s biggest
textile maker, said it has paid down its debts under the
country’s bankruptcy law to 5.6 billion pesos ($3 million).  The company made a payment of 13.8 billion pesos to the
country’s tax agency as part of its obligations under the
bankruptcy law, it said in a regulatory filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  